def_cn: 移居，迁徙(尤指到外地寻找工作或暂住一段时间)
def_en: If people migrate, they move from one place to another, especially in order to find work or to live somewhere for a short time.

def_cn: (鸟类、鱼类、兽类等随季节变化)迁徙
def_en: When birds, fish, or animals migrate, they move at a particular season from one part of the world or from one part of a country to another, usually in order to breed or to find new feeding grounds.
